\section{Echo Signatures}

Echo signals have been proposed as probes of horizon structure \cite{Cardoso2016,Cardoso2017}.

\begin{equation}
\Delta t_{\text{echo}} \approx 2\int_{r_0}^{r_{\text{ph}}} \frac{dr}{F(r)}
\end{equation}

\begin{equation}
\Delta t_{\text{echo}} \to \infty \quad \text{as} \quad \beta \to \beta_c
\end{equation}

